      <h1>How Brands Use Video Production to Promote Case Studies</h1>
      <p class="lead">Discover why video case studies matter for B2B success and how they help brands engage prospects, build trust, and showcase results.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>June 14, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 25, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
